{"tid":1754123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[運動繼續]做文宣，大遊行","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:44:10.000Z","uid":3776,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d93c1557ad725d3fb1f975debd5919af83394349","tid":1754123,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:10:31.000Z","msg":"區議會得勝只係一小步<br />\n但我地要既唔止黎樣<br />\n<br />\n所以繼續做文宣 對準五大訴求<br />\n我地要政府回應既係五大訴求<br />\n我地要既係<br />\n撤回惡法 撤回暴動定性 釋放所有義士 成立獨立調查委員會 同埋真普選 <br />\n未做齊以上五樣野 我地都唔會收手<br />\n<br />\n所以要脇住區選一役 黎一場大遊行<br />\n話比柒婆聽 我地無忘初心<br />\n堅持五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"94ee7b0e2c5725d56a770def70447055ad15eefe","tid":1754123,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac5d7ae668820494482a46c75d776cccbcbc84f3","tid":1754123,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3168a9951e2a4f2907c2b287b38e69fd4184271d","tid":1754123,"uid":129959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74580fe86fabf766ae1fa3e81ddbcdb02c71ab4","tid":1754123,"uid":87560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/pig_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e109e3595752d856fedfa667d4469fee496ba765","tid":1754123,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,